{
  "texts": [
    "For example, our taxonomy identifies \"limited access to internet data\" as a limitation; however, with the introduction of web browsing capabilities for GPT-4 in May 2023, this particular limitation no longer applies to that model.",
    "Given these ongoing developments, we strongly encourage future studies to test, update, and extend our taxonomy to ensure that it remains a relevant tool for categorizing LLM limitations in clinical and other high-stakes applications.",
    "Communications Medicine | (2025) 5:26"
  ]
}